article.headline: TCU 62, Air Force 50
article.story: FORT WORTH, Texas -- Zvonko Buljan scored 20 points to help lead TCU to a 62-50 victory over Air Force Wednesday night. Eight of Buljan's points came in the first 2:17 of the second half as the Horned Frogs took the lead for good. He hit back-to-back 3-pointers and added a layup. Keion Mitchem added 12 and Ronnie Moss contributed 10, including two 3-pointers, for TCU (14-12, 5-7 Mountain West). Andrew Henke had 13, Anwar Holland scored 12 and Evan Washington contributed 10 for Air Force (9-16, 0-12). Air Force led 23-22 at the half.
